Package structure

Interface List

All Superinterfaces:
Structure
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractList, CircularList, DoublyLinkedList, SinglyLinkedList, Vector
public interface List extends Structure
Interface describing lists. Lists are collections of data with a head and tail. Values may be added or removed from either end, as well as by value from the middle.
Author:
, 2001 duane a. bailey
